# lake-manifest.json is Lake's LOCKFILE and is deliberately TRACKED. Without it
# a fresh clone resolves the moving-branch deps to whatever they are that day,
# so the repo would not record what these proofs were actually checked against.
# These proofs back the consensus kernel that SHIPS in seal-host. CI cannot
# build at all without it.
